 libglfw-dev,
 libanttweakbar1.0-dev,
 libdsk3-dev | libdsk-dev,
 lib765-dev,
 libserial-dev (>= 0.5.2)

Package: cpctools-doc
Architecture: all
Description: Documentation for cpctools

